\section{Summary}

\begin{PauseHighLight}
  \begin{itemize}
  \item We can understand a lot of behaviours by understanding first
    order ODEs\pause
  \item Systems can exhibit fixed points, limit cycles (and even chaotic
    behaviour in enough dimensions)\pause
  \item We can study the stability of fixed points\pause
  \item The behaviour of systems can change radically as new fixed
    points emerge or fixed points become unstable\pause
  \end{itemize}
